---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 2rem;">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1 class="hero__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="hero__sub mx-auto">Last Updated: February 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding-top: 2rem; padding-bottom: 6rem;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; color: var(--clr-text-sub); line-height: 1.8;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        At RAGBase, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy ("Policy") describes how we collect, use, and protect the personal and corporate information of our users across Law, Finance, and Healthcare sectors. 
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">2. Core Privacy Guarantee (PII Redaction Firewall)</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        RAGBase employs a proprietary PII (Personally Identifiable Information) Redaction Firewall. Any documents uploaded to our platform are instantly scanned. Sensitive data (including but not limited to names, Social Security Numbers, financial account numbers, and Protected Health Information) is anonymized <strong>before</strong> it reaches our core reasoning models.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">3. Data Ownership and Usage</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <strong>You retain total ownership</strong> of your data. We do not use your uploaded case files, SEC records, patient histories, or any other proprietary data to train our foundational models. Your data is isolated within your designated workspace.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">4. Compliance</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Our infrastructure is designed to align with strict regulatory standards including HIPAA, GDPR, and principles of Attorney-Client Privilege. We utilize end-to-end encryption for data in transit and at rest.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--clr-text); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">5. Contact Us</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or data practices, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:contact@ragbasehq.com" style="color: var(--clr-primary); text-decoration: underline;">contact@ragbasehq.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
